name: Zinderlaw
body:
### Zinderlaw Theme.
This theme design was created exclusively for Zinder Law by Doug Santaniello. It is intended to be used only by Zinderlaw, however there are elements that require close watch so I wanted to be able to have a central location to update and deliver new content.

### Authors and Contributors
